Package com.pandora.general.objects

Class CellTimestep

java.lang.Object
com.pandora.general.objects.AbstractBaseObject
com.pandora.general.objects.CellTimestep
public class CellTimestep extends AbstractBaseObject
The CellTimestep class extends AbstractBaseObject and represents a specific time step associated with a geographical cell. It includes properties such as the initial and final state variable values, start and end times, and the geographical cell itself.

This class uses the Lombok library annotations Getter, Builder, and AllArgsConstructor to automatically generate getter methods, a builder, and an all-args constructor.
